A while ago,

35
00:02:02,100 --> 00:02:03,760
when I closed my eyes at night,

36
00:02:04,200 --> 00:02:05,040
as if I could hear

37
00:02:05,040 --> 00:02:08,800
the sound of the machines
clanking beside my ears,

38
00:02:08,960 --> 00:02:10,280
and in front of me…

39
00:02:12,000 --> 00:02:12,910
were all

40
