48
00:02:30,360 --> 00:02:32,280
- Great!
- Good!

49
00:02:37,960 --> 00:02:38,960
It's wonderful!

50
00:02:38,960 --> 00:02:40,590
The memorial museum is really wonderful!

51
00:02:43,400 --> 00:02:44,360
Thank you! Thank you!

52
00:02:45,360 --> 00:02:46,200
Xiaodong,

53
00:02:46,560 --> 00:02:47,400
right now,

54
00:02:47,400 --> 00:02:48,560
I'm so moved.

55
00:02:49,000 --> 00:02:50,750
I have to say a few words!

56
00:02:50,760 --> 00:02:51,800
Please, go ahead!

57
00:02:53,040 --> 00:02:54,080
What Xiaodong and the team

58
00:02:54,520 --> 00:02:55,560
have done, creating

59
00:02:56,150 --> 00:02:57,710
this memorial museum, is no small feat!

60
00:02:57,710 --> 00:02:58,960
By doing this,

61
00:02:59,280 --> 00:03:00,170
you've not only given

62
00:03:00,170 --> 00:03:02,150
the former employees of No. 9 Factory

63
00:03:02,840 --> 00:03:05,590
a way to remember the past,

64
00:03:06,430 --> 00:03:07,270
but also allowed

65
00:03:07,430 --> 00:03:08,360
Xiao Han,

66
00:03:08,680 --> 00:03:10,430
Jiayue, and the younger generation

67
00:03:10,590 --> 00:03:12,630
to understand how their grandparents

68
00:03:13,400 --> 00:03:14,240
and parents

69
00:03:14,960 --> 00:03:17,910
worked their way
up to where we are today.

70
00:03:17,910 --> 00:03:19,000
Yes, yes!

71
00:03:19,630 --> 00:03:22,680
Well said! Well said!

72
00:03:25,360 --> 00:03:26,800
Everyone, don't just stand here.

73
00:03:27,560 --> 00:03:29,470
Go and take a proper look
around the museum.

74
00:03:29,470 --> 00:03:31,590
If you see anything lacking,
do offer your suggestions.

75
00:03:31,590 --> 00:03:33,080
Alright? Go ahead.

76
00:03:33,190 --> 00:03:34,030
Come on.

77
00:03:34,800 --> 00:03:35,840
Have a good look around.

78
00:03:38,040 --> 00:03:39,280
- Grab a photo?
- Let's take a photo.

79
00:03:39,280 --> 00:03:40,260
- Sure.
- Let's take a photo.

80
00:03:43,290 --> 00:03:45,120
