I started working at the factory in 1974.

82
00:03:48,080 --> 00:03:50,150
This was my first job.

83
00:03:50,430 --> 00:03:52,430
It's the only factory I worked at.

84
00:03:56,030 --> 00:03:56,870
The basketball team!

85
